     </draw:image>
    </draw:frame><text:span text:style-name="T3">1. Business Plan</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P23">1.1 Executive Summary</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P7"><text:span text:style-name="T23">The project involves the development of a dynamic website for </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T26">&apos;Fiamma Fresca&apos;</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T23">, a takeaway pizzeria. The site allows customers to browse the menu, select a specific dough type for each pizza in their order, </text:span><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T23">and submit orders online. The project development spans from </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T26">09/03/2026 to 01/05/2026</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T23"> (40 working days). </text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P44">1.2 Key Product Features</text:p>
   <text:list text:style-name="L1">
    <text:list-item>
     <text:p text:style-name="P45"><text:span text:style-name="T26">Responsive Website:</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T23"> Built with PHP 8, CSS3, and JavaScript ES6+.</text:span></text:p>
    </text:list-item>
    <text:list-item>
     <text:p text:style-name="P45"><text:span text:style-name="T54">Individual Dough Selection:</text:span> Customers can choose a specific dough for every single pizza added to the cart (the project’s core innovation).</text:p>
    </text:list-item>
    <text:list-item>
     <text:p text:style-name="P45"><text:span text:style-name="T54">5 Dough Options:</text:span> Traditional Round, Whole Wheat, 72h Long Leavening, Spelt &amp; Semolina, and Gluten-Free.</text:p>
    </text:list-item>
    <text:list-item>
     <text:p text:style-name="P45"><text:span text:style-name="T54">Dynamic Cart:</text:span> Each row displays the pizza type + chosen dough + quantity + price.</text:p>
    </text:list-item>
    <text:list-item>
     <text:p text:style-name="P45"><text:span text:style-name="T54">MySQL Database:</text:span> Structured with 6 tables; dough selection is stored for every order line item.</text:p>
    </text:list-item>
    <text:list-item>
     <text:p text:style-name="P45"><text:span text:style-name="T54">Advanced Animations:</text:span> Powered by GSAP 3 + ScrollTrigger across all website sections.</text:p>
    </text:list-item>
    <text:list-item>
     <text:p text:style-name="P45"><text:span text:style-name="T54">Admin Panel:</text:span> Dedicated interface to view and update real-time order status</text:p>
    </text:list-item>
   </text:list>
   <text:list xml:id="list2109978199" text:style-name="WWNum1">
    <text:list-header>
     <text:p text:style-name="P43"/>
    </text:list-header>
   </text:list>
   <text:p text:style-name="P41"><text:span text:style-name="T19">1.3 </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T56">Market Analysis </text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P13">The food delivery market in Italy exceeds €<text:span text:style-name="T54">1.6 billion</text:span> annually, with pizzerias representing the dominant segment. Owning a proprietary website eliminates the <text:span text:style-name="T54">20-30% commissions</text:span> charged by third-party platforms like JustEat or Deliveroo. Providing dough customization per individual pizza is a high-value differentiator that increases the average ticket size and improves customer loyalty. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P40"><text:span text:style-name="T12">1.4 </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T58">Target Audience</text:span></text:p>
   <text:list text:style-name="L2">
    <text:list-item>
     <text:p text:style-name="P46"><text:span text:style-name="T26">Local Customers:</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T23"> Regular clients within a 5 km radius of the shop.</text:span></text:p>
    </text:list-item>
    <text:list-item>
     <text:p text:style-name="P46"><text:span text:style-name="T54">Families with Diverse Dietary Needs:</text:span> Allows a family to order, for example, one Gluten-Free pizza and several traditional ones in a single checkout.</text:p>
    </text:list-item>
    <text:list-item>
     <text:p text:style-name="P46"><text:span text:style-name="T54">Quality-Conscious Customers:</text:span> Clients seeking a premium, personalized dining experience.</text:p>
    </text:list-item>
    <text:list-item>
     <text:p text:style-name="P46"><text:span text:style-name="T54">Groups of Friends:</text:span> People with different nutritional preferences ordering together.</text:p>
    </text:list-item>
   </text:list>
   <text:list text:continue-list="list2109978199" text:style-name="WWNum1">
    <text:list-header>
     <text:p text:style-name="P43"/>
    </text:list-header>
   </text:list>
   <text:p text:style-name="P23">1.5 <text:span text:style-name="T53">SWOT </text:span>Anal<text:span text:style-name="T53">ysis</text:span> </text:p>
   <table:table table:name="Tabella1" table:style-name="Tabella1">
    <table:table-column table:style-name="Tabella1.A" table:number-columns-repeated="2"/>
    <table:table-row table:style-name="Tabella1.1">
     <table:table-cell table:style-name="Tabella1.A1" office:value-type="string">
      <text:p text:style-name="P27"><text:span text:style-name="Strong_20_Emphasis">STRENGTHS</text:span> </text:p>
     </table:table-cell>
     <table:table-cell table:style-name="Tabella1.B1" office:value-type="string">
      <text:p text:style-name="P27">WEAKNESSES </text:p>
     </table:table-cell>
    </table:table-row>
    <table:table-row table:style-name="Tabella1.1">
     <table:table-cell table:style-name="Tabella1.A2" office:value-type="string">
      <text:p text:style-name="P39"><text:span text:style-name="T47">+</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T44"> Individual dough selection: unique in the local market. <text:line-break/></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T47">+</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T44"> Zero commissions to third-party delivery platforms. <text:line-break/></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T47">+</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T44"> Real-time admin panel for efficient order management. </text:span></text:p>
     </table:table-cell>
     <table:table-cell table:style-name="Tabella1.A2" office:value-type="string">
      <text:p text:style-name="P39"><text:span text:style-name="T44">-</text:span> Annual hosting and domain costs. <text:span text:style-name="T44"><text:line-break/></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T47">-</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T44"> Slightly more complex UX due to dough selection steps. <text:line-break/></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T47">-</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T44"> Requirement for staff training on the new digital system. </text:span></text:p>
     </table:table-cell>
    </table:table-row>
   </table:table>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:span text:style-name="T11"/></text:p>
