   <text:p text:style-name="P55"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P52"><text:span text:style-name="T9">6. Installation Guide</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P54"><text:span text:style-name="T20">6.1 System Requirements</text:span></text:p>
   <text:list text:continue-numbering="true" text:style-name="WWNum1">
    <text:list-item>
     <text:p text:style-name="P42"><text:span text:style-name="T23">XAMPP &gt;= 8.0 (Apache + PHP 8.x + MySQL 8.x)</text:span></text:p>
    </text:list-item>
    <text:list-item>
     <text:p text:style-name="P42"><text:span text:style-name="T23">Browser <text:s/>(Chrome, Firefox, Edge)</text:span></text:p>
    </text:list-item>
    <text:list-item>
     <text:p text:style-name="P42"><text:span text:style-name="T23">Internet connection (to load GSAP and Google Fonts from CDN)</text:span></text:p>
    </text:list-item>
    <text:list-item>
     <text:p text:style-name="P42"><text:span text:style-name="T23">Disk space: ~5 MB</text:span></text:p>
    </text:list-item>
   </text:list>
   <text:p text:style-name="P54"><text:span text:style-name="T20">6.2 File Structure</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T23"><text:line-break/>After extracting the archive, the folder structure should be:</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P56"><text:span text:style-name="T50">la_fornace/<text:line-break/>├── index.php <text:s text:c="16"/>← Pagina principale<text:line-break/>├── css/<text:line-break/>│ <text:s text:c="2"/>└── style.css <text:s text:c="12"/>← Tutti gli stili<text:line-break/>├── js/<text:line-break/>│ <text:s text:c="2"/>└── main.js <text:s text:c="14"/>← Animazioni, carrello, AJAX<text:line-break/>├── php/<text:line-break/>│ <text:s text:c="2"/>├── config.php <text:s text:c="11"/>← Connessione PDO al database<text:line-break/>│ <text:s text:c="2"/>├── ordine.php <text:s text:c="11"/>← Endpoint ricezione ordini<text:line-break/>│ <text:s text:c="2"/>└── admin.php <text:s text:c="12"/>← Pannello amministratore<text:line-break/>└── sql/<text:line-break/> <text:s text:c="3"/>└── la_fornace.sql <text:s text:c="7"/>← Script creazione DB<text:line-break/></text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P54"><text:span text:style-name="T20">6.3 Step 1 — Place the files</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P54"><text:span text:style-name="T27"><text:s/>• Start XAMPP Control Panel → Start Apache and MySQL<text:line-break/>• Copy the &apos;la_fornace&apos; folder to: C:xampphtdocs (Windows) <text:line-break/></text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P54"><text:span text:style-name="T20">6.4 Step 2 — Create the Database</text:span></text:p>
   <text:list text:continue-numbering="true" text:style-name="WWNum1">
    <text:list-item>
     <text:p text:style-name="P42"><text:span text:style-name="T23">Open the browser and navigate to: http://localhost/phpmyadmin</text:span></text:p>
    </text:list-item>
    <text:list-item>
     <text:p text:style-name="P42"><text:span text:style-name="T23">Click on &apos;Import&apos; (top tab)</text:span></text:p>
    </text:list-item>
    <text:list-item>
     <text:p text:style-name="P42"><text:span text:style-name="T23">Select the file: la_fornace/sql/la_fornace.sql</text:span></text:p>
    </text:list-item>
    <text:list-item>
     <text:p text:style-name="P42"><text:span text:style-name="T23">Click &apos;Run&apos; — the following will be created automatically: database, all 6 tables</text:span></text:p>
    </text:list-item>
   </text:list>
   <text:p text:style-name="P53"><text:span text:style-name="T51"/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P54"><text:span text:style-name="T59"/></text:p>
